---
title: Creamy Spinach and Goat Cheese Rigatoni with Peas
description: Not all classics should be messed with, but when you add delicious veggies and tangy goat cheese to this pasta dish, you'll discover a little innovation can be a VERY good thing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-spinach-and-goat-cheese-rigatoni-bcd3a7ec.jpg
